calde de Tepexco, Puebla.]</ref>\n*January 25\n**Adalberto Rosas L\u00f3pez, pol\u00edtician from ([[Ciudad Obreg\u00f3n]]), Sonora; thrombosis.<ref>[http://www.kioscomayor.com/vernoticias.php?artid=75739&cat=33 Fallece Adalberto \"El Pel\u00f3n\" Rosas en Ciudad Obreg\u00f3n.]</ref>\n**Agust\u00edn Sauret (85), voice actor (\"Ned Flanders\" in ''[[The Simpsons]]'').<ref>{{cite web |website=El Universal |url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/espectaculos/television/2017/01/27/muere-agustin-sauret-la-voz-de-ned-flanders-en-los|title=Muere Agust\u00edn Sauret, la voz de \"Ned Flanders\" en \"Los Simpson\".}}</ref>\n**[[Ra\u00fal Valerio]], 90, actor ([[Por tu amor (telenovela)]], [[Clase 406]], [[La Verdad Oculta]], [[Imperio de Cristal]]).\n*January 26 \u2013 Javier Garc\u00eda Narro, businessperson and leader of [[Coparmex]] (a business association) in [[Saltillo]], Coahuila.<ref>[http://www.vanguardia.com.mx/articulo/fallece-el-empresario-saltillense-javier-e-garcia-narro-ex-presidente-de-la-coparmex Fallece el empresario saltillense Javier E. Garc\u00eda Narro, expresidente de la Coparmex Coahuila.]</ref>\n*January 27\n**Fredman Cruz Maldonado, singer; lung problems.<ref>[http://www.univision.com/musica/regional-mexicano/muere-el-cantante-del-grupo-pegasso Muere el cantante del Grupo Pegasso.]</ref>\n**Mario Palestina Moreno (45), baseball player; heart attack (b. 1971).<ref>[https://www.elsoldetlaxcala.com.mx/deportes-local/553804-muere-mario-palestina-moreno-destacado-beisbolista-apizaquense Muere Mario Palestina Moreno, destacado beisbolista apizaquense.]</ref>\n*January 28\n**Benjam\u00edn Cabral, filmmaker.<ref>[http://www.gacetamexicana.com/imcine-lamenta-fallecimiento-del-cineasta-benjamin-cabral/ Imcine lamenta el fallecimiento del cineasta Benjam\u00edn Cabral.]</ref>\n**V\u00edctor Hugo Salda\u00f1a Guti\u00e9rrez (22), soccer player; murdered (b. [[1994 in Mexico|November 8, 1994]]).<ref>{{cite web|website=Ascenso Mx |accessdate=Oct 14, 2019|title=