ournalist, essayist, playwright (b. 1951).<ref>{{citation|website=El Universal|title=Muere el escrito Eusebio Ruvalcaba |url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/cultura/letras/2017/02/8/muere-el-escritor-eusebio-ruvalcaba#imagen-1|language=es|accessdate=Oct 14, 2019}}</ref>\n*February 9 \u2013 [[Josefina Leiner]], actress (b. 1929).<ref name=exc>{{cite news |first= |last=|title=Fallece la actriz mexicana Josefina Leiner |url=http://www.excelsior.com.mx/funcion/2017/02/11/1145747 |work=[[Exc\u00e9lsior]] |publisher= |date=2017-02-11 |accessdate=2017-03-04}}</ref>\n*February 15 \u2013 [[Jos\u00e9 Sol\u00e9]], 87, stage actor and director ''([[Premio Nacional de Ciencias y Artes]])'' (b. July 28, 1929).<ref>{{cite news |newspaper=El Universal Cultura|url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/cultura/artes-escenicas/2017/02/17/emotivo-adios-al-maestro-jose-sole |title=Emotivo-adios-al-maestro-Jose Sol\u0117|language=es|date=February 17, 2017|accessdate=Oct 1, 2019}}</ref>\n*February 16 \u2013 [[Teresa del Conde]], art historian and critic (b. 1935).<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jornada.unam.mx/ultimas/2017/02/16/fallece-la-intelectual-teresa-del-conde|title=Fallece la intelectual Teresa del Conde|first=Merry|last=MacMasters|language=Spanish|website=jornada.unam.mx|date=16 February 2017|accessdate=18 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217145059/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/ultimas/2017/02/16/fallece-la-intelectual-teresa-del-conde|archive-date=2017-02-17|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n*February 21 \u2013 [[Neus Espresate Xirau]] (83), Spanish-born Mexican editor (founder of [[Ediciones Era]]); complicaciones respiratorias (n. 1934).<ref>[http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/cultura/letras/2017/02/21/fallece-neus-espresate-fundadora-de-ediciones-era Fallece Neus Espresate, fundadora de Ediciones Era.]</ref>\n*February 22\n**[[David B\u00e1rcena R\u00edos]], equestrian and modern pentathlete (b. 1941).\n**[[Ricardo Dom\u00ednguez]], 31, welterweig