os 69 a\u00f1os: uno de los grandes villanos de las telenovelas] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*November 20 \u2013 Silvestre de la Toba Camacho, 47, [[Ombudsman]] of the Human Rights Commission in [[Baja California Sur]]; murdered alongside his son Fernando de la Toba Lucero.<ref>https://www.jornada.com.mx/2017/11/21/politica/010n3pol</ref>\n*November 25\n**[[Jes\u00fas G\u00f3mez (equestrian)|Jes\u00fas G\u00f3mez]], 76, equestrian, Olympic bronze medalist ([[Equestrian at the 1980 Summer Olympics|1980]]).<ref>[https://www.esto.com.mx/318079-muere-el-jinete-jesus-gomez-portugal-montenegro/ Muere el jinete Jes\u00fas G\u00f3mez Portugal Montenegro] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**[[Rosario Green]], 76, economist, diplomat and politician, [[Secretariat of Foreign Affairs (Mexico)|Minister for Foreign Affairs]] (1998\u20132000) and [[Mexican Senate|Senator]] (2006\u20132012).<ref>[http://www.jornada.unam.mx/ultimas/2017/11/25/muere-ex-canciller-rosario-green-pena-lamenta-fallecimiento-4455.html Muere ex canciller Rosario Green; Pe\u00f1a lamenta fallecimiento] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171125213536/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/ultimas/2017/11/25/muere-ex-canciller-rosario-green-pena-lamenta-fallecimiento-4455.html |date=November 25, 2017 }} {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**[[Rosendo Huesca Pacheco]], 85, Roman Catholic prelate, Archbishop of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Puebla de los \u00c1ngeles|Puebla de los \u00c1ngeles]] (1977\u20132009).<ref>[http://www.proceso.com.mx/512603/fallece-rosendo-huesca-pacheco-vii-arzobispo-puebla Fallece Rosendo Huesca Pacheco, VII arzobispo de Puebla] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*November 26\n**[[Vicente Garc\u00eda Bernal]], 88, Roman Catholic prelate, Bishop of [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Ciudad Obreg\u00f3n|Ciudad Obreg\u00f3n]] (1988\u20132005).<ref>[http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/muere-obispo-emerito-vicente-garcia-bernal-en-sonora Muere Obispo Em\u00e9rito Vicente Garc\u00eda Bernal en Sonora] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**[[\u00d3sca