.com.mx/estados/asesinan-tiros-al-alcalde-de-petatlan-guerrero</ref>\n**Luis Abraham Gonz\u00e1lez Contreras (31), photographer y reporter; murdered.\n**Gerardo Olavarrieta Le\u00f3n, hotel owner (\"Suites Kokai\", \"Plaza Kokai\", and \"Condominios Kokai\") in [[Cancun]], Quintana Roo.<ref>http://www.elquintanaroo.mx/wp/fallece-empresario-hotelero-de-cancun/</ref>\n**Mario Stern (81), composer and acad\u00e9mic (b. 1936).<ref>https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/cultura/musica/fallece-el-compositor-mexicano-mario-stern</ref>\n*December 31\n**Regino D\u00edaz Redondo, journalist (''[[Exc\u00e9lsior]]'').\n**Juan Gonz\u00e1lez G\u00f3mez (\"Juan Cotz\"), 63, painter from [[Chamula|San Juan Chamula]], Chiapas (b. June 24, 1954).<ref>https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/muere-el-pintor-juan-gallo-en-su-casa-de-chiapas</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Mexico}}\n*[[Timeline of Mexican history]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Years in Mexico}}\n{{Year in North America|2017}}\n{{Latin America and the Caribbean topic|2017 in}}\n\n[[Category:2017 in Mexico| ]]\n[[Category:2010s in Mexico]]\n[[Category:Years of the 21st century in Mexico]]\n[[Category:2017 by country|Mexico]]\n", "text_old": "{{Year in Mexico|2017}}\n\nThis is a list of events that happened in [[2017]] in Mexico.\n\n==Incumbents==\n* [[President of Mexico|President]]: [[Enrique Pe\u00f1a Nieto]]\n{{For|the list of governors of the states of Mexico|Category:Lists of governors of States of Mexico}}\n\n==Events==\n*18 January \u2013 [[Colegio Americano del Noreste shooting]]\n*14 March \u2013 A mass grave site of more than 250 people is discovered in Palmas de Abajo, Veracruz.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/investigators-find-more-250-skulls-mexico-graves-n733916|title=Investigators Find More Than 250 skulls in Mexico Graves|last=|first=|date=15 March 2017|website=nbcnews.com|access-date=15 March 2017}}</ref>\n*7 September \u2013 [[2017 Chiapas earthquake|A magnitude 8.1]] [[earthquake]] 