1167373 Fallece promotor cultural de Tuxpan.]</ref>\n**Olegario Contreras Rubio, radio announcer in Sinaloa; heart problems.<ref>[http://www.lineadirectaportal.com/publicacion.php?noticia=321265 Fallece Olegario Contreras, \u00edcono de la locuci\u00f3n en Sinaloa.]</ref>\n**Analy Loera, businesswoman and cultural promoter; brain and lung cancer.<ref>[http://www.dossierpolitico.com/vernoticias.php?artid=184376&relacion=&tipo=Noticias&categoria=1 Muere Analy Loera.]</ref>\n*January 3\n**[[Cecilia Gonz\u00e1lez G\u00f3mez]], 55, politician, Deputy (2012-2915); heart attack (b. 1961).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.informador.com.mx/mexico/2017/700103/6/fallece-diputada-cecilia-gonzalez-gomez.htm |title=Fallece diputada Cecilia Gonz\u00e1lez G\u00f3mez |language=Spanish|accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref>\n**Luc\u00eda Eugenia Torres Pereda, journalist.<ref>[http://pulsoslp.com.mx/2017/01/03/fallece-lucy-torres-periodista-y-vocera-de-la-cedh/ Fallece Lucy Torres, periodista y vocera de la CEDH.]</ref>\n*January 5\n**Marco Francisco Gonz\u00e1lez Meza, public servant, accidente de tr\u00e1fico.<ref>[http://www.campeche.com.mx/noticias/nacional/fallece-delegado-de-cisen-en-tamaulipas-epn-externo-condolencias/317072 Fallece delegado de Cisen en Tamaulipas, EPN extern\u00f3 condolencias.]</ref>\n**[[Alfonso Humberto Robles Cota]], [[Roman Catholic]] bishop of Tepic (b. 1931).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/brobles.html |title=Bishop Alfonso Humberto Robles Cota |accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref>\n**Ces\u00e1reo V\u00edctor Santiago L\u00f3pez, pol\u00edtician from Oaxaca; murdered.<ref>[http://www.radioformula.com.mx/notas.asp?Idn=652935&idFC=2017 Asesinan a balazos a exs\u00edndico municipal de San Pedro Amuzgos (Oaxaca).]</ref>\n**Carmen S\u00e1nchez Gal\u00e1n (45), public servant; complicaciones post-operative complications.<ref>[http://periodicocorreo.com.mx/fallece-carmen-sanchez-galan/ Fallece Carmen S\u00e1nchez Gal\u00e1n.]</ref>\n*Janu