ional mexicano amanece de luto; muere Jorge Robles.]</ref>\n*January 30 \u2013 [[Fidel Briano]] (72), lawyer and journalist.<ref>[http://lajornadasanluis.com.mx/destacada/fallecio-fidel-briano/ Falleci\u00f3 Fidel Briano.]</ref>\n*January 31 \n**Pedro Koh Cim\u00e9, Yucatan pol\u00edtician; murdered.<ref>[http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/estados/2017/01/31/apunalan-regidor-del-pri-en-yucatan-ya-hay-detenidos Apu\u00f1alan a regidor del PRI en Yucat\u00e1n; ya hay detenidos.]</ref>\n**Jos\u00e9 Luis Lagunes L\u00f3pez, public servant; c\u00e1ncer.<ref>[http://noreste.net/noticia/muere-jose-luis-lagunes-lopez/ Muere Jos\u00e9 Luis Lagunes L\u00f3pez.]</ref>\n\n===February===\n*February 3 \u2013 [[Lorenzo Servitje]], 98, businessman and philanthropist, co-founder of [[Grupo Bimbo]] (b. November 20, [[1918 in Mexico|1918]].<ref>{{cite web|website=SDP Negocios|language=es|title=Muere Lorenzo Servitje, fundador de Grupo Bimbo|date=Feb 3, 2017|accessdate=Oct 13, 2019|url=https://www.sdpnoticias.com/negocios/fundador-servitje-lorenzo-grupo-muere.html}}</ref> \n*February 7 \u2013 [[Eusebio Ruvalcaba]] (65), writer (''Un hilito de sange''), journalist, essayist, playwright (b. 1951).<ref>{{citation|website=El Universal|title=Muere el escrito Eusebio Ruvalcaba |url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/cultura/letras/2017/02/8/muere-el-escritor-eusebio-ruvalcaba#imagen-1|language=es|accessdate=Oct 14, 2019}}</ref>\n*February 9 \u2013 [[Josefina Leiner]], actress (b. 1929).<ref name=exc>{{cite news |first= |last=|title=Fallece la actriz mexicana Josefina Leiner |url=http://www.excelsior.com.mx/funcion/2017/02/11/1145747 |work=[[Exc\u00e9lsior]] |publisher= |date=2017-02-11 |accessdate=2017-03-04}}</ref>\n*February 15 \u2013 [[Jos\u00e9 Sol\u00e9]], 87, stage actor and director ''([[Premio Nacional de Ciencias y Artes]])'' (b. July 28, 1929).<ref>{{cite news |newspaper=El Universal Cultura|url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/cultura/artes-escenicas/2017/02/17/emo