untualizando.com/fallece-el-profesor-fernando-sarabia-guamuchilense-distinguido/ Fallece el profesor Fernando Sarabia, guamuchilense distinguido.]</ref>\n\n===June===\n*June 2 \u2013 Armando Mendoza Duarte (48), pol\u00edtician; murdered (b. 1969).\n*June 3\n**Juan Robinson Bours, businessman from [[Ciudad Obreg\u00f3n]], Sonora; [[Alzheimer's disease]] (b. December 25, 1928)<ref>https://www.infocajeme.com/general/2017/06/fallece-juan-robinson-bours/</ref>\n**Antonio Sarabia (72), writer (''Tres pies al gato'') (b. June 10, 1944).\n*June 5\n**[[Eduardo Catarino Dircio]], politician (Morena) from [[Tixtla de Guerrero (municipality)|Tixtla de Guerrero municipality]], Guerrero; killed by state police.<ref>{{citation|website=Regeneration|title=Polic\u00edas estatales asesinan a l\u00edder de Morena en Tixtla, Guerrero|date=June 5, 2017|accessdate=Oct 17, 2019|language=es|trans-title=State police kill leader of Morena in Tixtla, Guerrero|url=https://regeneracion.mx/policias-asesinan-lider-morena-guerrero/}}</ref>\n**Eleazar Vargas Lara, community leader and politician from [[Iguala]], Guerrero; murdered.<ref>https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/estados/2017/06/6/asesinan-dirigente-de-colonos-en-iguala-guerrero</ref>\n**Ana Winocur (44), journalist; pancreatitis (b. October 1972).<ref>https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/galeria/espectaculos/farandula/2017/06/5/fallece-la-conductora-y-periodista-ana-winocur#imagen-1</ref>\n*June 6 \u2013 Jorge Ortiz Murray, leader of fishermen in [[Mazatlan]]; heart attack.<ref>https://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones/view/fallece-jorge-ortiz-murray-dirigente-pesquero-en-mazatlan-1086105</ref>\n*June 8 \n**[[Antonio Medell\u00edn]], 75, Mexican actor (''[[Tres veces Ana]]'', ''[[Porque el amor manda]]'', ''[[Cuando me enamoro (telenovela)|Cuando me enamoro]]'').<ref>[http://www.latintimes.com/antonio-medellin-dead-75-tres-veces-ana-actor-dies-actors-guild-confirms-419102 Antonio Medell\u00edn Dead At 75: 'Tres Veces Ana' Actor Dies, Actors 